        "97": {
            "h2[0]": "Features That Fuel Your Passion",
            "p[0]": "Explore cutting-edge facilities and top-tier equipment tailored specifically for serious athletes and dedicated lifters. Our gym is the ultimate space for those who want to push their limits and achieve their peak performance.",
            "h3[0]": "Unmatched Equipment",
            "p[1]": "Train with state-of-the-art machines and free weights designed for maximum effectiveness and durability.",
            "h3[1]": "Tailored Training Zones",
            "p[2]": "Experience training environments engineered for powerlifting and bodybuilding, allowing you to focus solely on your goals.",
            "h3[2]": "Expert Coaching",
            "p[3]": "Receive guidance from experienced coaches who understand the demands of serious training and are committed to helping you excel.",
            "h3[3]": "Community Support",
            "p[4]": "Join a network of like-minded individuals who share your passion for strength and discipline, pushing each other to succeed.",
            "h3[4]": "Flexible Hours",
            "p[5]": "Access the gym at hours that fit your schedule, ensuring you can train when it suits you best.",
            "h3[5]": "Membership Options",
            "p[6]": "Choose from a variety of plans that cater to your needs, from casual lifters to serious competitors."
        },
        "151": {
