            "p[0]": "About Us",
            "h3[0]": "Powerlifting Focused",
            "p[1]": "We specialize in powerlifting and bodybuilding, offering a gritty atmosphere that reflects our commitment to serious training. Here, excellence is not just a goal; it's a way of life.",
