            "p[2]": "Our gym is equipped with top-tier equipment tailored for serious lifters. Each piece is chosen to support your journey toward greatness, providing everything you need to push your limits.",
            "h3[2]": "Expert Coaching",
            "p[3]": "Our coaching programs are designed to empower you with knowledge and motivation. With experienced trainers by your side, you’ll gain the discipline to excel and the skills to conquer your goals.",
